1
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:06,719
Lao Sun

2
00:00:07,519 --> 00:00:08,119
Tell you what

3
00:00:08,839 --> 00:00:11,480
I'll give you 500,000, in cash.

4
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:14,919
Hey, hey, hey, a million.

5
00:00:15,279 --> 00:00:16,000
Just let me go

6
00:00:16,399 --> 00:00:18,879
Have you forgotten what you've done?

7
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:13,959
Baby

8
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:20,920
I thought you'd abandoned me

9
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,239
How could I?

10
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,120
I'm here, don't be afraid

11
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,879
What on earth happened?

12
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,760
Someone broke into my home

13
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,159
He wants to kill me

14
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,599
I'm scared to death

15
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,159
Someone wants to kill you?

16
00:01:36,359 --> 00:01:37,359
Who wants to kill you?

17
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:40,560
He, he, he...

18
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,760
He forced me to hand over all our

19
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:45,079
external dealings and account records

20
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,000
He said I had backups

21
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:50,719
Baby

22
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,599
Just give it to him

23
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:54,120
Saving your life is what matters

24
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,359
What's wrong?

25
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:02,040
This has something to do with you, doesn't it?

26
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:05,560
After all I've done for you these years,

27
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,599
You suspect me?

28
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:09,240
Have you been using me all along?

29
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,319
Listen to me

30
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,080
I won't listen

31
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,680
I've put up with this for years

32
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,159
I don't want to take it anymore

33
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,639
I've never doubted you

34
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,039
I love you so much

35
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,360
Do you really love me?

36
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,479
Or am I just a pawn to you,

37
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:25,599
to be moved around as you please?

38
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:28,439
Silly, what nonsense are you saying?

39
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,439
You're right

40
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:36,199
I am a complete and utter fool

41
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,759
Ever since we got together,

42
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,840
I've worked day and night on your projects

43
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,479
When your parents got sick,

44
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,800
I ran around contacting hospitals

45
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,919
Even your wife's birthday cake,

46
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:50,400
I delivered it to your doorstep myself

47
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,719
You know how much I love you

48
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,039
I promised you

49
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,479
Once we save enough money,

50
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:58,240
we would run away together.

51
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,439
To live in our own little world

52
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,199
Did you forget?

53
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:02,240
It's all just lies

54
00:03:02,879 --> 00:03:04,039
Don't be rash

55
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:06,960
I really haven't lied to you

56
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:09,639
Every word I said is the truth

57
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,800
Trust me

58
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,199
I know

59
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,159
Their investigation has you on edge

60
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:28,759
But I promise you,

61
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,759
I'll handle it

62
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:32,360
I won't let anyone

63
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,680
or anything

64
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,280
hurt you

65
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,000
You better keep your word.

66
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,879
You have to save me

67
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,240
Everything I've done has been for you

68
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,719
I don't want to go to prison

69
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:48,199
And I don't want them to kill me either

70
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,360
I promise you

71
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:57,879
Don't worry

72
00:03:58,879 --> 00:03:59,919
I give you my word

73
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,080
Come

74
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:08,800
Sit here

75
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:16,519
Have a drink, calm down

76
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:34,639
Can you swear to love me forever?

77
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,480
I swear

78
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,519
I'll love you my whole life

79
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:49,319
Hey, what are you doing?

80
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,600
I, Su Zhuang,

81
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,600
I swear to heaven

82
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,680
I'll protect you my whole life

83
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,639
If I ever fail you,

84
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,399
I'll jump from here

85
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:00,240
and fall to my death

86
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,399
Don't say such foolish things

87
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,279
Get down from there, now

88
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,240
It's dangerous up there

89
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:04,920
If you don't believe me,

90
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,680
I'll jump

91
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:09,160
right off this ledge now

92
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:12,879
Don't! I believe you, I believe you!

93
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,959
I believe every word

94
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,519
You have to believe me too

95
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,879
Come down, hurry

96
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:25,439
I really haven't done anything to wrong you

97
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:27,600
Take us away

98
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,360
I promise you

99
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:40,000
I'll promise you anything

100
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,079
Really? That's wonderful!

101
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,560
Be careful!

102
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:49,079
It's dangerous!

103
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,240
Sun, take a good look at who I am.

104
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,800
What do you want?

105
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,319
Lao Wu.

106
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:51,639
Where's the money?

107
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:52,560
What money?

108
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:54,720
Fifty-five million.

109
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:58,839
I gambled it.

110
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,040
I lost.

111
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,120
It's all gone.

112
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,199
You blew 55 million in one night?

113
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,439
It's really all gone.

114
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:16,519
Fine.

115
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,879
Let's see what that hide of yours is worth.

116
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,560
What are you doing?

117
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,040
Calm down!

118
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:27,879
Don't do anything crazy.

119
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,800
How about a million for this leg?

120
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:40,480
Lao Sun.

121
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:41,839
Tell you what.

122
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:45,199
I'll give you 500,000, in cash.

123
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,759
Hey, hey, hey, a million.

124
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,879
Just let me go.

125
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:52,600
Have you forgotten what you've done?

126
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:02,639
Help!

127
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:08,839
How about two million for this leg?

128
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:14,319
I really don't have any money.

129
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,800
How much do you want anyway?

130
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,879
Fifteen million.

131
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,759
Not a cent less.

132
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,560
We agreed on...

133
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,199
...ten million, didn't we?

134
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,800
Why is it five million more?

135
00:08:28,639 --> 00:08:30,439
I only have ten million.

136
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,120
You broke the deal first.

137
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:37,639
Now the bosses have cops on their tail.

138
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,360
We're not making you cough up everything.

139
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,559
Ah, it's cutting into me!

140
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,639
Consider it a favor to you.

141
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,240
I...

142
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:49,159
I don't have money. I only have ten million.

143
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,000
Ten million.

144
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,200
Fine.

145
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,440
One arm.

146
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:57,879
Worth a million.

147
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,320
No, no!

148
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,039
Three.

149
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,519
Two.

150
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,039
One.

151
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:07,360
I'll pay, I'll pay, I'll pay!

152
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,200
I'll give you fifteen million.

153
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:11,879
Are we good now?

154
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,039
You're sure it's this car, right?

155
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:23,480
Yes.

156
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,840
This car is registered under Jingwen Group.

157
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,399
Jingwen Group?

158
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,919
Xu Wenwen's Jingwen Group?

159
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,120
The Xu Wenwen who gave us...

160
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,519
...leads on the Liu Xiang Case?

161
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,399
That famous female entrepreneur.

162
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,759
The club in Wuzhuang might be hers too.

163
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,360
Xu Wenwen.

164
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,879
Ma Shijiang.

165
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,320
What's the connection between these two?

166
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,559
This is a serious matter.

167
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,200
We can't just speculate.

168
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,759
Once the Shen Qing case has leads...

169
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,080
...then we'll look into this.

170
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,759
That night, he was lying on this bed.

171
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,320
What time did he come in?

172
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,679
It was just past 9:30 when I entered.

173
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:40,519
He must have arrived just shortly before.

174
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,080
Then please,

175
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,720
walk us through everything that happened after.

176
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,200
Don't leave out a single detail.

177
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:49,960
Okay.

178
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,679
Sir, my name is Xiao Li.

179
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:10,360
I'll be serving you tonight.

180
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,840
If you're satisfied,

181
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,679
when you leave,

182
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:14,279
don't forget to leave a positive review.

183
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:15,559
Thank you, sir.

184
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,279
Quite professional.

185
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:22,399
Come on.

186
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,759
Let's see what you've got.

187
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:27,600
Don't worry, sir.

188
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,879
I'll make sure you're nice and comfortable.

189
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,480
I've been busy all day.

190
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,600
My whole body is stiff.

191
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:33,879
Loosen me up, quick.

192
00:11:45,759 --> 00:11:47,240
But after less than ten minutes,

193
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,639
he was almost asleep.

194
00:11:54,879 --> 00:11:55,559
Sir.

195
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,080
Sir.

196
00:11:59,639 --> 00:12:00,279
Hmm?

197
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,879
Sir, how's my technique?

198
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:10,759
Sir, have you been really tired lately?

199
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,399
I've even had insomnia.

200
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:16,600
But I have to say, with your massage,

201
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:18,519
I'm starting to feel sleepy.

202
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:21,159
If you come a few more times,

203
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,440
these hands of mine

204
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,919
can cure any illness you have.

205
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:27,799
Aren't you full of yourself.

206
00:12:29,279 --> 00:12:31,679
In a bit, if I fall asleep,

207
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,720
don't wake me up.

208
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:36,039
But you'll need to turn over.

209
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,960
Just let me sleep,

210
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:41,840
here,

211
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:44,759
I'll add an hour for you.

212
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,879
That doesn't seem right, sir.

213
00:12:48,039 --> 00:12:49,399
What's not right about it?

214
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:51,120
As long as I'm happy.

215
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:53,039
All right, sir.

216
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,559
Then I'll add another hour.

217
00:12:54,559 --> 00:12:55,919
That'd be 12:42.

218
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:58,279
Can I come wake you at 12:30?

219
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:01,960
Perfect.

220
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,360
Are clients like Lin Xiaohu common?

221
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:07,879
Very rare.

222
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,399
Maybe one or two a year.

223
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:12,440
Usually, even if a client is fast asleep,

224
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:13,919
we still have to keep massaging.

225
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,000
What time did you leave his room?

226
00:13:31,799 --> 00:13:32,559
A little after ten.

227
00:13:32,799 --> 00:13:34,240
And until past midnight,

228
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,399
you didn't come back in?

229
00:13:35,519 --> 00:13:37,440
No, I locked the room.

230
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,879
The key was with me the whole time.

231
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:41,919
Does Lin Xiaohu come to your place often?

232
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:43,799
I wouldn't know.

233
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:46,360
It was my first time serving him, anyway.

234
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,240
Jiang Han, pull the car under the window.

235
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:52,120
Make it quick.

236
00:13:55,039 --> 00:13:57,120
Please step out and lock the door.

237
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:57,639
Thank you.

238
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,440
Okay.

239
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,720
Let's go. To Shen Qing's place, now!

240
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,320
Take the Emergency lane.

241
00:14:45,879 --> 00:14:47,320
Turn right ahead, take the back road.

242
00:15:11,679 --> 00:15:12,360
Can you get up there?

243
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,080
Shifu, that's a bit high.

244
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,559
Or is it you who can't make it up?

245
00:15:16,559 --> 00:15:17,960
I'm asking if you can get up there.

246
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,840
Me? Of course I can.

247
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:20,519
It's a piece of cake.

248
00:15:20,519 --> 00:15:21,759
Quit talking and get moving.

249
00:15:39,679 --> 00:15:41,440
Shifu, let me give you a hand.

250
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:44,240
No need. If you can climb up, so can I.

251
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,399
Why didn't you pull me up?

252
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:02,799
Come on Shifu, that's not fair.

253
00:16:02,879 --> 00:16:04,120
You told me not to pull you up.

254
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:04,879
Hurry up.

255
00:16:04,879 --> 00:16:06,080
Before someone mistakes us for thieves.

256
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,159
It really is a bit high.

257
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,320
Give me a hand after all.

258
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,320
Not bad, Shifu.

259
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,559
You talk too much.

260
00:16:28,399 --> 00:16:29,120
Hey, stop right there!

261
00:16:29,399 --> 00:16:30,120
Shifu, this...

262
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:30,799
Ignore him.

263
00:16:30,799 --> 00:16:31,279
Stop!

264
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:31,799
Run!

265
00:16:34,519 --> 00:16:35,120
Stop!

266
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,559
Stop running! Halt!

267
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,000
Captain.

268
00:16:46,759 --> 00:16:47,360
That's him.

269
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,360
Who's there?

270
00:16:49,919 --> 00:16:51,000
Grab him, take him to the station.

271
00:16:51,759 --> 00:16:52,840
Hey, don't hit me!

272
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:56,639
It's a misunderstanding.

273
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:57,759
Police!

274
00:16:58,200 --> 00:16:59,000
Police on duty.

275
00:17:00,639 --> 00:17:01,200
Get him!

276
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:03,159
Police on duty!

277
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,960
Isn't that Captain Li?

278
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:10,880
On a case?

279
00:17:12,839 --> 00:17:13,720
Pull back, pull back!

280
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:19,400
Hold on, Shifu.

281
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:21,000
What's going on?

282
00:17:21,119 --> 00:17:22,599
That guard's pitchfork was right in your face,

283
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:23,519
and you didn't say a word.

284
00:17:23,559 --> 00:17:24,640
Well, I had you with me, didn't I?

285
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,359
Shifu.

286
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:29,160
You finally realize how important I am, huh?

287
00:17:29,279 --> 00:17:29,880
Let me tell you,

288
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:30,880
as long as I'm around...

289
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,960
Shh.

290
00:17:33,279 --> 00:17:34,799
I really mean what I say.

291
00:17:34,799 --> 00:17:35,480
Stop right there.

292
00:17:36,039 --> 00:17:37,599
We ran from the foot spa to here

293
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:38,799
in eighteen minutes.

294
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,279
At night with no traffic,

295
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:41,599
fifteen minutes tops.

296
00:17:43,519 --> 00:17:45,240
So Lin Xiaohu had time to commit the crime.

297
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:47,880
And the route we ran, even if cameras worked,

298
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,960
would barely catch anyone on tape.

299
00:17:50,839 --> 00:17:53,000
But deduction isn't evidence.

300
00:17:56,039 --> 00:17:56,759
Exactly.

301
00:17:58,279 --> 00:17:59,079
Give me some advice.

302
00:18:02,839 --> 00:18:04,039
My advice is...

303
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:06,559
keep looking for clues.

304
00:18:08,599 --> 00:18:09,319
Let him go.

305
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:11,279
What?

306
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,640
Just let him walk like that?

307
00:18:13,799 --> 00:18:14,559
There's no evidence.

308
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:15,839
We have to let him go.

309
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:19,200
Shifu, that's not like you.

310
00:18:19,559 --> 00:18:21,200
Aren't you usually so clever?

311
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,680
Why go silent at the crucial moment?

312
00:18:23,039 --> 00:18:25,200
Don't you always say you're a genius too?

313
00:18:25,799 --> 00:18:26,920
Got any ideas to crack him?

314
00:18:33,079 --> 00:18:34,960
Give him rope, right?

315
00:18:36,119 --> 00:18:36,960
I get it now.
